<segment id="62" parent="63" relname="circumstance">After an attack in the London streets last year on British soldier Lee Rigby ,</segment>
<segment id="63" parent="1062" relname="span">two men were sentenced on Wednesday .</segment>
<segment id="64" parent="1001" relname="joint">The leader of the attack , Michael Adebolajo , was sentenced to life behind bars .</segment>
<segment id="65" parent="1001" relname="joint">Michael Adebowale was given a life sentence ,</segment>
<segment id="66" parent="1066" relname="span">but with the possibility of parole</segment>
<segment id="67" parent="66" relname="circumstance">after serving a minimum of 45 years .</segment>
<segment id="68" parent="69" relname="attribution">In court , the two Islamic converts indicated</segment>
<segment id="69" parent="1068" relname="span">the killing was for Allah .</segment>
<segment id="70" parent="1070" relname="sequence">Bystanders watched Adebolajo and Adebowale hit Rigby with a car</segment>
<segment id="71" parent="1070" relname="sequence">then butcher him with a meat cleaver and knives .</segment>
<segment id="72" parent="1072" relname="span">The attack was recorded on closed-circuit TV and by bystanders .</segment>
<segment id="73" parent="72" relname="elaboration">Both men were convicted of murder in December 2013 .</segment>
